eloPy - a python input driver for elo touchscreens
==================================================

Standalone pure-Python userspace driver for elo serial touchscreens.
Based on psychopy's iohub elo touch driver.


Dependencies:
-------------
You need a recent version of pyserial
pip install --upgrade pyserial
numpy

Optional dependencies:
----------------------
pygame (required for visualize demo)
pymouse (required for elomouse demo)
for pymouse on linux: python-xlib
for pymouse on windows: pywin32 and pyHook
for pymouse on mac os: Quartz and AppKit


Running the application:
------------------------
See main.py as starting point

visualize.py  Draw the press events in a pygame window
elomouse.py   Redirect touch events to the desktop as mouse presses